```plantuml
@startuml danielfm_prometheus-for-developers

actor Developer as dev
participant "Sample Node.js App" as app
participant Prometheus
participant Alertmanager
participant Grafana

dev -> app: Starts application
app -> app: Exposes /metrics endpoint
app -> app: Generates sample metrics (request durations)

dev -> Prometheus: Configures scrape targets
Prometheus -> app: Scrapes metrics (HTTP GET /metrics)
app --> Prometheus: Returns metrics data

Prometheus -> Prometheus: Evaluates alert rules
Prometheus -> Alertmanager: Sends alerts (when triggered)
Alertmanager -> Alertmanager: Processes alerts (deduplication, grouping)
Alertmanager -> dev: Notifies via configured channels

dev -> Grafana: Configures Prometheus datasource
Grafana -> Prometheus: Queries metrics data
Prometheus --> Grafana: Returns metrics
Grafana -> dev: Displays visualizations

@enduml
```